@crypto_coiner shall be one of the members of the PPC First Liquidity Operations Team (FLOT). @crypto_coiner will coordinate with other members of PPC FLOT, and members of FSRT if necessary, to defend the peg. @crypto_coiner promises to be a part of PPC FLOT for at least one year and to abide by all shareholder motions governing the use of funds. @crypto_coiner will be able to respond to any request for signing within 48 hours of its proposal; shareholders must be promptly informed of exceptions.

Compensation for @crypto_coiner will occur in 90-day cycles, for a total of 4 cycles. By the end of each cycle, a total of amount of 190 NBT shall be paid to @crypto_coiner, conditional on satisfactory performance, which shall be measured in terms of his presence, effort and contribution. @crypto_coiner reserves the right to withdraw from his service if he does not receive the full amount of compensation by the end of any cycle or by personal discretion.

